# Database Package Structure Guide

The database schemas and related configurations for the project are located within the `packages/db` directory.

- **Schemas**: All database table definitions and schemas can be found in [packages/db/src/schemas/](mdc:packages/db/src/schemas). This directory is the central place for understanding the data model of the application.

Refer to the files within this directory to understand the structure of different database entities.
